    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"Rest in the peace that comes from letting go...\" That is a beautiful thought, yet so terrifying. Every morning I wake up and the weight of his absence feels like iron on my chest. Is it truly wrong to want the silence to finally become permanent? To simply stop the clock?",
